WEBVTT

00:00:59.640 --> 00:01:00.976
make eye contact,

00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:04.239
and finally, my ability to speak.

00:01:05.280 --> 00:01:06.496
While in hospital,

00:01:06.520 --> 00:01:09.096
I desperately wanted to go home.

00:01:09.120 --> 00:01:12.416
I said to my mother, "When home?"

00:01:12.440 --> 00:01:16.896
Those were the last words
I ever spoke with my own voice.

00:01:16.920 --> 00:01:20.736
I would eventually fail every test
for mental awareness.

00:01:20.760 --> 00:01:23.576
My parents were told
I was as good as not there.

00:01:23.600 --> 00:01:28.216
A vegetable, having the intelligence
of a three-month-old baby.

00:01:28.240 --> 00:01:31.896
They were told to take me home
and try to keep me comfortable